}\\,sr^{-1}$ for a NS merger rate of $10^{-7}\\,\\rm\nMpc^{-3}\\,yr^{-1}$, overlapping with IceCube's current sensitivity and within\nthe reach of next-generation neutrino telescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2017 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Sep 2017 21:56:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-10"}
