edle is also assessed\nanalytically in terms of spheroidal wave functions. The dynamic behavior of the\nneedle in solution is found to be identical to needle Lorentz systems, where a\ntracer needle explores a quenched disordered array of other needles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jul 2017 09:39:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-17"}
